data.description: Premium lot connected to greenspace! Open concept with HUGE kitchen that offers breakfast room, counter bar, island, granite countertops, SS appliances, luxury plank vinyl flooring throughout 1st flr! Generously sized primary bedroom with garden shower & walk-in closet! Fenced-in backyard, 4ft extended garage, cul-de-sac street, pool community, and other amenities! Home offers a lot of natural light!
